# Renderer (`src/renderer`)

- No Node.js APIs; use `window.api` from preload IPC only.
- UI state: Zustand stores under `stores/`; keep components focused.
- i18n: add EN and AR keys in `i18n/` when adding user-visible copy; Arabic enables RTL on `<html>`.
- **Manuscript (Ouroboros loop)** ships via [`OuroborosLoopWorkspace`](../components/loop/OuroborosLoopWorkspace.tsx) (`appSurface === 'loop'`). Legacy [`ManuscriptAudit/AuditView`](../components/ManuscriptAudit/) is **retired** — do not remount that layout; extend the loop per `docs/PRODUCT.md`.
- Engine-heavy work belongs in `src/engine/`, not duplicated in the renderer.
- Run `npm test` and `npm run lint` after substantive changes.
